{
  "video_id": "D4vjGSiRGKY",
  "title": "100 solutions to reverse global warming | Chad Frischmann",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13359.0,
      "end_time": 14856.0,
      "text": "Hello."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14880.0,
      "end_time": 18616.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to introduce you to a word you may never have heard before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18640.0,
      "end_time": 20256.0,
      "text": "but you ought to know:"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20280.0,
      "end_time": 21520.0,
      "text": "drawdown."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22760.0,
      "end_time": 26880.0,
      "text": "Drawdown is a new way of thinking about and acting on global warming."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27840.0,
      "end_time": 31176.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a goal for a future that we want,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31200.0,
      "end_time": 35400.0,
      "text": "a future where reversing global warming is possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36440.0,
      "end_time": 38656.0,
      "text": "Drawdown is that point in time"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38680.0,
      "end_time": 43960.0,
      "text": "when atmospheric concentrations of greenhouse gases begin to decline"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43120.0,
      "end_time": 44519.0,
      "text": "on a year-to-year basis."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45400.0,
      "end_time": 47416.0,
      "text": "More simply, it&#39;s that point"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47440.0,
      "end_time": 52680.0,
      "text": "when we take out more greenhouse gases than we put into Earth&#39;s atmosphere."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 54400.0,
      "end_time": 57879.0,
      "text": "Now, I know we&#39;re all concerned about climate change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 58800.0,
      "end_time": 61736.0,
      "text": "but climate change is not the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 61760.0,
      "end_time": 65456.0,
      "text": "Climate change is the expression of the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 65480.00000000001,
      "end_time": 71200.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the feedback of the system of the planet telling us what&#39;s going on."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 72360.0,
      "end_time": 75560.0,
      "text": "The problem is global warming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 75800.0,
      "end_time": 79376.0,
      "text": "provoked by the increasing concentrations of greenhouse gases"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 79400.0,
      "end_time": 81400.0,
      "text": "caused by human activity."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 81880.0,
      "end_time": 83455.0,
      "text": "So how do we solve the problem?"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 83480.0,
      "end_time": 87720.0,
      "text": "How do we begin the process of reversing global warming?"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 89120.0,
      "end_time": 92896.0,
      "text": "The only way we know how is to draw down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 92920.0,
      "end_time": 95456.0,
      "text": "to avoid putting greenhouse gases up"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 95480.0,
      "end_time": 97440.0,
      "text": "and to pull down what&#39;s already there."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 99800.0,
      "end_time": 100336.0,
      "text": "I know."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 100360.0,
      "end_time": 103560.0,
      "text": "Given the current situation, it sounds impossible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 104960.0,
      "end_time": 107880.0,
      "text": "but humanity already knows what to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 109160.0,
      "end_time": 112735.0,
      "text": "We have real, workable technologies and practices"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 112760.0,
      "end_time": 114200.0,
      "text": "that can achieve drawdown."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 115480.0,
      "end_time": 116766.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s already happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 117760.0,
      "end_time": 121856.0,
      "text": "What we need is to accelerate implementation"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 121880.0,
      "end_time": 123896.0,
      "text": "and to change the discourse"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 123920.0,
      "end_time": 128400.0,
      "text": "from one of fear and confusion, which only leads to apathy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 129720.0,
      "end_time": 133336.0,
      "text": "to one of understanding and possibility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 133360.0,
      "end_time": 135160.0,
      "text": "and, therefore, opportunity."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 136560.0,
      "end_time": 138960.0,
      "text": "I work for an organization called Project Drawdown."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 139880.0,
      "end_time": 141295.0,
      "text": "And for the last four years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 141320.0,
      "end_time": 145176.0,
      "text": "together with a team of researchers and writers from all over the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 145200.0,
      "end_time": 148576.0,
      "text": "we have mapped, measured and detailed"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 148600.0,
      "end_time": 151799.0,
      "text": "100 solutions to reversing global warming."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 152920.0,
      "end_time": 155456.0,
      "text": "Eighty already exist today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 155480.0,
      "end_time": 159320.0,
      "text": "and when taken together, those 80 can achieve drawdown."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 160240.0,
      "end_time": 163776.0,
      "text": "And 20 are coming attractions, solutions on the pipeline,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 163800.0,
      "end_time": 165736.0,
      "text": "and when they come online,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 165760.0,
      "end_time": 167519.0,
      "text": "will speed up our progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 168880.0,
      "end_time": 170656.0,
      "text": "These are solutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 170680.0,
      "end_time": 175616.0,
      "text": "that are viable, scalable and financially feasible."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 175640.0,
      "end_time": 177760.0,
      "text": "And they do one or more of three things:"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 178760.0,
      "end_time": 185136.0,
      "text": "replace existing fossil fuel-based energy generation with clean, renewable sources;"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 185160.0,
      "end_time": 188616.0,
      "text": "reduce consumption through technological efficiency"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 188640.0,
      "end_time": 189880.0,
      "text": "and behavior change;"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 190760.0,
      "end_time": 195136.0,
      "text": "and to biosequester carbon in our plants&#39; biomass and soil"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 195160.0,
      "end_time": 197536.0,
      "text": "through a process we all learn in grade school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 197560.0,
      "end_time": 199240.0,
      "text": "the magic of photosynthesis."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 199920.0,
      "end_time": 203160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s through a combination of these three mechanisms"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 203400.0,
      "end_time": 205799.0,
      "text": "that drawdown becomes possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 206680.0,
      "end_time": 207880.0,
      "text": "So how do we get there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 208480.0,
      "end_time": 210480.0,
      "text": "Well, here&#39;s the short answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 211480.0,
      "end_time": 215935.0,
      "text": "This is a list of the top 20 solutions to reversing global warming."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 215960.0,
      "end_time": 217416.0,
      "text": "Now, I&#39;ll go into some detail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 217440.0,
      "end_time": 220000.0,
      "text": "but take a few seconds to look over the list."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 225000.0,
      "end_time": 227960.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s eclectic, I know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 227120.0,
      "end_time": 230416.0,
      "text": "from onshore wind turbines to educating girls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 230440.0,
      "end_time": 234000.0,
      "text": "from plant-rich diets to rooftop solar technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 234680.0,
      "end_time": 236416.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s break it down a little bit."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 236440.0,
      "end_time": 239576.0,
      "text": "To the right of the slide, you&#39;ll see figures in gigatons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 239600.0,
      "end_time": 242550.0,
      "text": "or billions of tons."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 242800.0,
      "end_time": 245376.0,
      "text": "That represents the total equivalent carbon dioxide"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 245400.0,
      "end_time": 247136.0,
      "text": "reduced from the atmosphere"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 247160.0,
      "end_time": 251790.0,
      "text": "when the solution is implemented globally over a 30-year period."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 251840.0,
      "end_time": 255216.0,
      "text": "Now, when we think about climate solutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 255240.0,
      "end_time": 258176.0,
      "text": "we often think about electricity generation."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 258200.0,
      "end_time": 262135.0,
      "text": "We think of renewable energy as the most important set of solutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 262160.0,
      "end_time": 264816.0,
      "text": "and they are incredibly important."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 264840.0,
      "end_time": 267335.0,
      "text": "But the first thing to notice about this list"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 267360.0,
      "end_time": 270800.0,
      "text": "is that only five of the top 20 solutions relate to electricity."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 272399.0,
      "end_time": 275560.0,
      "text": "What surprised us, honestly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 275800.0,
      "end_time": 278640.0,
      "text": "was that eight of the top 20 relate to the food system."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 280400.0,
      "end_time": 284496.0,
      "text": "The climate impact of food may come as a surprise to many people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 284520.0,
      "end_time": 288575.0,
      "text": "but what these results show is that the decisions we make every day"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 288600.0,
      "end_time": 292160.0,
      "text": "about the food we produce, purchase and consume"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 292400.0,
      "end_time": 294856.0,
      "text": "are perhaps the most important contributions"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 294880.0,
      "end_time": 298800.0,
      "text": "every individual can make to reversing global warming."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 299200.0,
      "end_time": 303560.0,
      "text": "And how we manage land is also very important."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 303800.0,
      "end_time": 306960.0,
      "text": "Protecting forests and wetlands"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 306120.0,
      "end_time": 310416.0,
      "text": "safeguards, expands and creates new carbon sinks"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 310440.0,
      "end_time": 313456.0,
      "text": "that directly draw down carbon."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 313480.0,
      "end_time": 315240.0,
      "text": "This is how drawdown can happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 316480.0,
      "end_time": 320256.0,
      "text": "And when we take food and land management together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 320280.0,
      "end_time": 326736.0,
      "text": "12 of the top 20 solutions relate to how and why we use land."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 326760.0,
      "end_time": 332159.0,
      "text": "This fundamentally shifts traditional thinking on climate solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 333360.0,
      "end_time": 335960.0,
      "text": "But let&#39;s go to the top of the list,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 335120.0,
      "end_time": 338560.0,
      "text": "because I think what&#39;s there may also surprise you."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 338800.0,
      "end_time": 340560.0,
      "text": "The single most impactful solution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 341560.0,
      "end_time": 344816.0,
      "text": "according to this analysis, would be refrigeration management,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 344840.0,
      "end_time": 349536.0,
      "text": "or properly managing and disposing of hydrofluorocarbons, also known as HFCs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 349560.0,
      "end_time": 354440.0,
      "text": "which are used by refrigerators and air conditioners to cool the air."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 355640.0,
      "end_time": 357976.0,
      "text": "We did a great job with the Montreal Protocol"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 358000.0,
      "end_time": 361256.0,
      "text": "to limit the production of chlorofluorocarbons, CFCs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 361280.0,
      "end_time": 363296.0,
      "text": "because of their effect on the ozone layer."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 363320.0,
      "end_time": 365896.0,
      "text": "But they were replaced by HFCs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 365920.0,
      "end_time": 370960.0,
      "text": "which are hundreds to thousands of times more potent a greenhouse gas"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 370120.0,
      "end_time": 371320.0,
      "text": "than carbon dioxide."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 372120.0,
      "end_time": 376520.0,
      "text": "And that 90 gigatons reduced is a conservative figure."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 377480.0,
      "end_time": 381896.0,
      "text": "If we were to account for the impact of the Kigali agreement of 2016,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 381920.0,
      "end_time": 384856.0,
      "text": "which calls for the phaseout of hydrofluorocarbons"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 384880.0,
      "end_time": 388400.0,
      "text": "and replace them with natural refrigerants, which exist today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 389880.0,
      "end_time": 394776.0,
      "text": "this number could increase to 120, to nearly 200 gigatons"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 394800.0,
      "end_time": 397160.0,
      "text": "of avoided greenhouse gases."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 397400.0,
      "end_time": 398840.0,
      "text": "Maybe you&#39;re surprised, as we were."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 400160.0,
      "end_time": 403376.0,
      "text": "Now, before going into some details of specific solutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 403400.0,
      "end_time": 406000.0,
      "text": "you may be wondering how we came to these calculations."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 407400.0,
      "end_time": 410560.0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, we collected a lot of data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 410800.0,
      "end_time": 413496.0,
      "text": "and we used statistical analysis to create ranges"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 413520.0,
      "end_time": 416496.0,
      "text": "that allow us to choose reasonable choices"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 416520.0,
      "end_time": 418880.0,
      "text": "for every input used throughout the models."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 420160.0,
      "end_time": 424160.0,
      "text": "And we chose a conservative approach, which underlies the entire project."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 425120.0,
      "end_time": 427136.0,
      "text": "All that data is entered in the model,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 427160.0,
      "end_time": 430296.0,
      "text": "ambitiously but plausibly projected into the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 430320.0,
      "end_time": 432796.0,
      "text": "and compared against what we would have to do anyway."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 433680.0,
      "end_time": 438256.0,
      "text": "The 84 gigatons reduced from onshore wind turbines, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 438280.0,
      "end_time": 441296.0,
      "text": "results from the electricity generated from wind farms"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 441320.0,
      "end_time": 445280.0,
      "text": "that would otherwise be produced from coal or gas-fired plants."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 446400.0,
      "end_time": 452256.0,
      "text": "We calculate all the costs to build and to operate the plants"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 452280.0,
      "end_time": 453840.0,
      "text": "and all the emissions generated."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 454960.0,
      "end_time": 458640.0,
      "text": "The same process is used to compare recycling versus landfilling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 459560.0,
      "end_time": 462176.0,
      "text": "regenerative versus industrial agriculture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 462200.0,
      "end_time": 465280.0,
      "text": "protecting versus cutting down our forests."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 466880.0,
      "end_time": 470936.0,
      "text": "The results are then integrated within and across systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 470960.0,
      "end_time": 472536.0,
      "text": "to avoid double-counting"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 472560.0,
      "end_time": 475920.0,
      "text": "and add it up to see if we actually get to drawdown."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 477720.0,
      "end_time": 480960.0,
      "text": "OK, let&#39;s go into some specific solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 482400.0,
      "end_time": 485160.0,
      "text": "Rooftop solar comes in ranked number 10."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 486560.0,
      "end_time": 489136.0,
      "text": "When we picture rooftop solar in our minds"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 489160.0,
      "end_time": 495200.0,
      "text": "we often envision a warehouse in Miami covered in solar panels."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 496800.0,
      "end_time": 500455.0,
      "text": "But these are solutions that are relevant in urban and rural settings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 500480.0,
      "end_time": 502496.0,
      "text": "high and low-income countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 502520.0,
      "end_time": 504159.0,
      "text": "and they have cascading benefits."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 505360.0,
      "end_time": 510960.0,
      "text": "This is a family on a straw island in Lake Titicaca"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 510120.0,
      "end_time": 512376.0,
      "text": "receiving their first solar panel."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 512400.0,
      "end_time": 515895.0,
      "text": "Before, kerosene was used for cooking and lighting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 515919.0,
      "end_time": 517439.0,
      "text": "kerosene on a straw island."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 518200.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523560.00000000006,
      "text": "So by installing solar, this family is not only helping to reduce emissions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 523799.99999999994,
      "end_time": 525720.0,
      "text": "but providing safety and security for their household."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 526760.0,
      "end_time": 528799.0,
      "text": "And tropical forests tell their own story."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 529679.0,
      "end_time": 533736.0,
      "text": "Protecting currently degraded land in the tropics"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 533760.0,
      "end_time": 536336.0,
      "text": "and allowing natural regeneration to occur"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 536360.0,
      "end_time": 539600.0,
      "text": "is the number five solution to reversing global warming."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 540760.0,
      "end_time": 543520.0,
      "text": "We can think of trees as giant sticks of carbon."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 544680.0,
      "end_time": 548376.0,
      "text": "This is drawdown in action every year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 548400.0,
      "end_time": 552400.0,
      "text": "as carbon is removed from the atmosphere through photosynthesis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 552880.0,
      "end_time": 557800.0,
      "text": "which converts carbon dioxide to plants&#39; biomass and soil organic carbon."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 559240.0,
      "end_time": 562960.0,
      "text": "And we need to rethink how we produce our food"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 562120.0,
      "end_time": 564000.0,
      "text": "to make it more regenerative."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 564720.0,
      "end_time": 568416.0,
      "text": "There are many ways to do this, and we researched over 13 of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 568440.0,
      "end_time": 570656.0,
      "text": "but these aren&#39;t new ways of producing food."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 570680.0,
      "end_time": 574239.0,
      "text": "They have been practiced for centuries, for generations."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 575640.0,
      "end_time": 579560.0,
      "text": "But they are increasingly displaced by modern agriculture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 579800.0,
      "end_time": 582456.0,
      "text": "which promotes tillage, monocropping"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 582480.0,
      "end_time": 587776.0,
      "text": "and the use of synthetic fertilizers and pesticides which degrade the land"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 587800.0,
      "end_time": 590599.0,
      "text": "and turn it into a net emitter of greenhouse gases."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 591360.0,
      "end_time": 594176.0,
      "text": "Regenerative agriculture, on the other hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 594200.0,
      "end_time": 596896.0,
      "text": "restores soil health and productivity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 596920.0,
      "end_time": 598776.0,
      "text": "increases yield,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 598800.0,
      "end_time": 600496.0,
      "text": "improves water retention,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 600520.0,
      "end_time": 604456.0,
      "text": "benefits smallholder farmers and large farming operations alike"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 604480.0,
      "end_time": 606440.0,
      "text": "and brings carbon back to the land."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 607480.0,
      "end_time": 611776.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a win-win-win-win-win."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 611800.0,
      "end_time": 613959.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 615400.0,
      "end_time": 616959.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not just how we produce food,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 617920.0,
      "end_time": 619415.0,
      "text": "but what we consume"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 619440.0,
      "end_time": 621960.0,
      "text": "that has a massive impact on global warming."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 622600.0,
      "end_time": 625176.0,
      "text": "A plant-rich diet is not a vegan or a vegetarian diet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 625200.0,
      "end_time": 627280.0,
      "text": "though I applaud any who make those choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 628240.0,
      "end_time": 631536.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a healthy diet in terms of how much we consume,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 631560.0,
      "end_time": 634280.0,
      "text": "and particularly how much meat is consumed."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 635160.0,
      "end_time": 636776.0,
      "text": "In the richer parts of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 636800.0,
      "end_time": 638000.0,
      "text": "we overconsume."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 638800.0,
      "end_time": 641335.0,
      "text": "However, low-income countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 641360.0,
      "end_time": 644896.0,
      "text": "show an insufficient caloric and protein intake."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 644920.0,
      "end_time": 646616.0,
      "text": "That needs rebalancing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 646640.0,
      "end_time": 648736.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s in the rebalancing"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 648760.0,
      "end_time": 651376.0,
      "text": "that a plant-rich diet becomes the number four solution"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 651400.0,
      "end_time": 652760.0,
      "text": "to reversing global warming."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 654600.0,
      "end_time": 658920.0,
      "text": "Moreover, approximately a third of all food produced is not eaten,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 659920.0,
      "end_time": 664839.0,
      "text": "and wasted food emits an astounding eight percent of global greenhouse gases."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 666320.0,
      "end_time": 668896.0,
      "text": "We need to look where across the supply chain"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 668920.0,
      "end_time": 670640.0,
      "text": "these losses and wastage occurs."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 671240.0,
      "end_time": 674176.0,
      "text": "In low-income countries, after food leaves the farm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 674200.0,
      "end_time": 676856.0,
      "text": "most food is wasted early in the supply chain"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 676880.0,
      "end_time": 679120.0,
      "text": "due to infrastructure and storage challenges."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 679920.0,
      "end_time": 682815.0,
      "text": "Food is not wasted by consumers in low-income countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 682840.0,
      "end_time": 684760.0,
      "text": "which struggle to feed their population."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 686800.0,
      "end_time": 688936.0,
      "text": "In the developed world, instead, after food leaves the farm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 688960.0,
      "end_time": 691336.0,
      "text": "most food is wasted at the end of the supply chain"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 691360.0,
      "end_time": 692816.0,
      "text": "by markets and consumers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 692840.0,
      "end_time": 694976.0,
      "text": "and wasted food ends up in the landfill"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 695000.0,
      "end_time": 696200.0,
      "text": "where it emits methane"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 697720.0,
      "end_time": 699120.0,
      "text": "as it decomposes."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 700760.0,
      "end_time": 702720.0,
      "text": "This is a consumer choice problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 703520.0,
      "end_time": 704880.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not a technology issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 706360.0,
      "end_time": 708656.0,
      "text": "Preventing food waste from the beginning"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 708680.0,
      "end_time": 710790.0,
      "text": "is the number three solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 711760.0,
      "end_time": 714160.0,
      "text": "But here&#39;s the interesting thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 714400.0,
      "end_time": 716415.0,
      "text": "When we look at the food system as a whole"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 716440.0,
      "end_time": 718896.0,
      "text": "and we implement all the production solutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 718920.0,
      "end_time": 720360.0,
      "text": "like regenerative agriculture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 721200.0,
      "end_time": 723376.0,
      "text": "and we adopt a plant-rich diet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 723400.0,
      "end_time": 725295.0,
      "text": "and we reduce food waste,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 725320.0,
      "end_time": 731176.0,
      "text": "our research shows that we would produce enough food on current farmland"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 731200.0,
      "end_time": 735216.0,
      "text": "to feed the world&#39;s growing population a healthy, nutrient-rich diet"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 735240.0,
      "end_time": 737400.0,
      "text": "now until 2050 and beyond."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 738720.0,
      "end_time": 742360.0,
      "text": "That means we don&#39;t need to cut down forests for food production."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 743320.0,
      "end_time": 747880.0,
      "text": "The solutions to reversing global warming are the same solutions to food insecurity."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 749640.0,
      "end_time": 753400.0,
      "text": "Now, a solution that often does not get talked enough about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 754720.0,
      "end_time": 755920.0,
      "text": "family planning."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 756760.0,
      "end_time": 759336.0,
      "text": "By providing men and women the right to choose"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 759360.0,
      "end_time": 763376.0,
      "text": "when, how and if to raise a family"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 763400.0,
      "end_time": 766536.0,
      "text": "through reproductive health clinics and education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 766560.0,
      "end_time": 769415.0,
      "text": "access to contraception"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 769440.0,
      "end_time": 771800.0,
      "text": "and freedom devoid of persecution"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 772680.0,
      "end_time": 776719.0,
      "text": "can reduce the estimated global population by 2050."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 777960.0,
      "end_time": 780560.0,
      "text": "That reduced population means reduced demand"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 780800.0,
      "end_time": 785360.0,
      "text": "for electricity, food, travel, buildings and all other resources."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 786560.0,
      "end_time": 787935.0,
      "text": "All the energy and emissions"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 787960.0,
      "end_time": 790376.0,
      "text": "that are used to produce that higher demand"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 790400.0,
      "end_time": 793935.0,
      "text": "is reduced by providing the basic human right"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 793960.0,
      "end_time": 797640.0,
      "text": "to choose when, how and if to raise a family."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 798680.0,
      "end_time": 803790.0,
      "text": "But family planning cannot happen without equal quality of education"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 804160.0,
      "end_time": 806319.0,
      "text": "to girls currently being denied access."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 807320.0,
      "end_time": 809576.0,
      "text": "Now, we&#39;ve taken a small liberty here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 809600.0,
      "end_time": 814560.0,
      "text": "because the impact of universal education"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 814800.0,
      "end_time": 816560.0,
      "text": "and family planning resources"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 816800.0,
      "end_time": 819160.0,
      "text": "are so inextricably intertwined"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 819400.0,
      "end_time": 821199.0,
      "text": "that we chose to cut it right down the middle."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 822360.0,
      "end_time": 826976.0,
      "text": "But taken together, educating girls and family planning"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 827000.0,
      "end_time": 830256.0,
      "text": "is the number one solution to reversing global warming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 830280.0,
      "end_time": 834880.0,
      "text": "reducing approximately 120 billion tons of greenhouse gases."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 838120.0,
      "end_time": 839320.0,
      "text": "So is drawdown possible?"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 840240.0,
      "end_time": 843656.0,
      "text": "The answer is yes, it is possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 843680.0,
      "end_time": 845400.0,
      "text": "but we need all 80 solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 846480.0,
      "end_time": 848976.0,
      "text": "There are no silver bullets or a subset of solutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 849000.0,
      "end_time": 850480.0,
      "text": "that are going to get us there."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 851480.0,
      "end_time": 854560.0,
      "text": "The top solutions would take us far along the pathway,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 854800.0,
      "end_time": 856280.0,
      "text": "but there&#39;s no such thing as a small solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 857800.0,
      "end_time": 858280.0,
      "text": "We need all 80."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 859800.0,
      "end_time": 860366.0,
      "text": "But here&#39;s the great thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 861240.0,
      "end_time": 864576.0,
      "text": "We would want to implement these solutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 864600.0,
      "end_time": 866920.0,
      "text": "whether or not global warming was even a problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 868120.0,
      "end_time": 872840.0,
      "text": "because they have cascading benefits to human and planetary well-being."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 874360.0,
      "end_time": 879520.0,
      "text": "Renewable electricity results in clean, abundant access to energy for all."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 881760.0,
      "end_time": 884536.0,
      "text": "A plant-rich diet, reduced food waste"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 884560.0,
      "end_time": 888880.0,
      "text": "results in a healthy global population with enough food and sustenance."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 890400.0,
      "end_time": 891959.0,
      "text": "Family planning and educating girls?"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 893200.0,
      "end_time": 895816.0,
      "text": "This is about human rights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 895840.0,
      "end_time": 897400.0,
      "text": "about gender equality."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 898800.0,
      "end_time": 902695.0,
      "text": "This is about economic improvement and the freedom of choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 902720.0,
      "end_time": 903920.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 905680.0,
      "end_time": 909976.0,
      "text": "Regenerative agriculture, managed grazing, agroforestry, silvopasture"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 910000.0,
      "end_time": 913936.0,
      "text": "restores soil health, benefits farmers"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 913960.0,
      "end_time": 916160.0,
      "text": "and brings carbon back to the land."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 917320.0,
      "end_time": 921216.0,
      "text": "Protecting our ecosystems also protects biodiversity"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 921240.0,
      "end_time": 922880.0,
      "text": "and safeguards planetary health"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 923840.0,
      "end_time": 925360.0,
      "text": "and the oxygen that we breathe."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 926720.0,
      "end_time": 929960.0,
      "text": "Its tangible benefits to all species are incalculable."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 931240.0,
      "end_time": 935296.0,
      "text": "But one last point, because I know it&#39;s probably on everybody&#39;s mind;"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 935320.0,
      "end_time": 937120.0,
      "text": "how much is this going to cost?"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 938520.0,
      "end_time": 943415.0,
      "text": "Well, we estimate that to implement all 80 solutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 943440.0,
      "end_time": 947456.0,
      "text": "would cost about 29 trillion dollars over 30 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 947480.0,
      "end_time": 949456.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s just about a trillion a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 949480.0,
      "end_time": 952416.0,
      "text": "Now, I know that sounds like a lot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 952440.0,
      "end_time": 956560.0,
      "text": "but we have to remember that global GDP is over 80 trillion every year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 957480.0,
      "end_time": 961560.0,
      "text": "and the estimated savings from implementing these solutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 961800.0,
      "end_time": 964696.0,
      "text": "is 74 trillion dollars, over double the costs."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 964720.0,
      "end_time": 968400.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a net savings of 44 trillion dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 971000.0,
      "end_time": 972320.0,
      "text": "So drawdown is possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 973320.0,
      "end_time": 975200.0,
      "text": "We can do it if we want to."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 976200.0,
      "end_time": 981760.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not going to cost that much, and the return on that investment is huge."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 983520.0,
      "end_time": 984880.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s the welcome surprise."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 986280.0,
      "end_time": 988199.0,
      "text": "When we implement these solutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 989200.0,
      "end_time": 991696.0,
      "text": "we shift the way we do business"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 991720.0,
      "end_time": 996616.0,
      "text": "from a system that is inherently exploitative and extractive"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 996640.0,
      "end_time": 1001199.0,
      "text": "to a new normal that is by nature restorative and regenerative."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 1003280.0,
      "end_time": 1007136.0,
      "text": "We need to rethink our global goals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 1007160.0,
      "end_time": 1009776.0,
      "text": "to move beyond sustainability"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 1009800.0,
      "end_time": 1011935.0,
      "text": "towards regeneration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 1011960.0,
      "end_time": 1014640.0,
      "text": "and along the way reverse global warming."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 1015440.0,
      "end_time": 1016656.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 1016680.0,
      "end_time": 1020839.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}